inputs.text: A hyper-realistic portrait of a ageless elvish woman with silver-white hair, violet eyes, ethereal features. She is wearing flowing robes made of living moss and flowers, natural crown of branches.  The setting is ancient enchanted forest with glowing mushrooms and magical light. Her expression conveys mystical, protective, connected to nature.  Technical specifications: Shot with 24-70mm f/2.8 for versatile framing with professional sharpness, using three-point lighting setup with key light, fill light, and rim light, composed with three-quarter view showing elegant neck line and shoulder angle.  The image should have professional studio quality, sharp focus on the eyes, beautiful skin texture details, perfect anatomy, and cinematic lighting. Style: photorealistic, high fashion photography, editorial quality, award-winning portrait photography.
